# Goldens are derived from assets/* by gen_goldens.bat — too large
# for plain git (silesia .slz files exceed GitHub's 100 MB per-file
# limit; total ~2.4 GiB across web/enwik8/silesia × L1-L5).
#
# Mirrors the existing assets/* gitignore pattern: source data is
# user-provided locally, derived artifacts are user-regenerated.

# Ignore everything in this dir by default.
*

# Track the regeneration script + expected-hash manifest + this
# .gitignore itself + any documentation we add.
!.gitignore
!gen_goldens.bat
!manifest.sha256
!README.md
